    "However, the implications of these principles (e.g., what privacy demands, or even what counts as privacy) cannot be analyzed in the abstract, because they will differ across types of relationships.",
    "Just as 'respect for privacy' means something different in close friendships or family relationships than it does in formal employment relationships, so, too, might it mean different things for an AI romantic 'partner,' AI therapist, or AI work assistant.",
